pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: tools-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 45, 200, 22]
    content:
      style: "$label"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>TOOLS & PLATFORMS</p>

  - elementId: tools-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 75, 700, 40]
    content:
      style: "$heading"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Tools of the Trade: Figma & InVision</p>

  - elementId: tools-accent-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 125, 50, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: figma-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 155, 555, 220]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardFill"

  - elementId: figma-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [90, 175, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fab:figma"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: figma-name
    elementType: text
    bounds: [140, 175, 200, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 24
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Figma</p>

  - elementId: figma-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [90, 225, 495, 130]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$secondary"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>All-in-one design tool with built-in prototyping, real-time collaboration, and component-based workflow. Best when design and prototype live in one place.</p>

  - elementId: invision-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [665, 155, 555, 220]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardFill"

  - elementId: invision-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [695, 175, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fab:invision"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: invision-name
    elementType: text
    bounds: [745, 175, 200, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 24
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>InVision</p>

  - elementId: invision-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [695, 225, 495, 130]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$secondary"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Dedicated prototyping platform with advanced animation, user testing integration, and seamless developer handoff. Ideal for complex interactions.</p>

  - elementId: both-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 400, 300, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$accent"
      letterSpacing: 2
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>BOTH SUPPORT</p>

  - elementId: both-features
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 440, 1160, 55]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$secondary"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, middle]
      text: |
        <p>Clickable hotspots  ·  Screen transitions  ·  Overlay panels  ·  Scrollable areas  ·  Smart animate  ·  Real-time preview  ·  Shareable links</p>

  - elementId: tip-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 560, 1160, 80]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [6000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$muted"

  - elementId: tip-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [90, 580, 28, 28]
    iconName: "fas:lightbulb"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: tip-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [130, 570, 1060, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$primary"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, middle]
      text: |
        <p><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Start with low-fidelity prototypes and progressively add detail as you validate concepts.</p>

  - elementId: tools-bottom-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 690, 1160, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
